    "In snow conditions, the air can be considered as a low-humidity medium with high-reflectivity snowflakes.",
    "We adopt the approach [67], and utilize β to represent the snowfall rate.",
    "• Motion blur.",
    "This effect is common in images when the vehicle moves rapidly.",
    "For simplicity, we use a convolution with Gaussian kernel to simulate this blurring effect."
